					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13676644#post-4777459</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13676644/scp-5982#post-4777459</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 18 Sep 2020 15:09:03 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TheConqueringEnigma</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6121874</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Primary complaints:</p> <p>-The commune has no anomalous traits besides the weird carrot. Why is it the SCP?<br /> -The preacher is the anomalous object and escaped, so why is this neutralized?<br /> -Nothing happened here involving containing an SCP. It's just a raid on a compound run by a weird bender.</p> <p>The writing is good and engaging, but the focus of the article just doesn't see right.</p> <p>-1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13676644#post-4770234</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13676644/scp-5982#post-4770234</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 08 Sep 2020 14:52:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Gentleman Thief</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1782925</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This bit seems odd:</p> <blockquote> <p><strong>RENO:</strong> For hours?</p> <p><strong>WHITE:</strong> He is- was, a good preacher.</p> <p><strong>RENO:</strong> Then the flash of light. What was that about?</p> <p><strong>WHITE</strong>: He is- was, a good preacher.</p> <p><strong>RENO:</strong> Jesus nuts usually are.</p> </blockquote> <p>Is it a typo?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
